SMBMS 5.0
技术点：
1、resultMap高级查询（collection）
与association原理相似只是collection得到的是一个结果集而association得到的是一个对象！
具体配置如下
<resultMap type="User" id="userAddressList">
		<id property="id" column="id" />
		<result property="userCode" column="userCode" />
		<result property="userName" column="userName" />
		<collection property="addresslist" ofType="Address">
			<id property="id" column="a_id" />
			<result property="contact" column="contact" />
			<result property="addressDesc" column="addressDesc" />
			<result property="tel" column="tel" />
			<result property="userId" column="userId" />
		</collection>
</resultMap>
<select id="getUserAddressList" parameterType="Integer"
		resultMap="userAddressList">
		SELECT u.userName,u.id,a.id AS a_id,a.addressDesc,a.tel,a.contact
		FROM smbms_user u,smbms_address a
		WHERE a.userId=#{id} AND u.id=a.userId
</select>
2、collection代码重用
<resultMap type="User" id="userAddressList">
		<id property="id" column="id" />
		<result property="userCode" column="userCode" />
		<result property="userName" column="userName" />
		<collection property="addresslist" ofType="Address" resultMap="addressList"></collection>
</resultMap>
<resultMap type="Address" id="addressList">
		<id property="id" column="a_id" />
		<result property="contact" column="contact" />
		<result property="addressDesc" column="addressDesc" />
		<result property="tel" column="tel" />
		<result property="userId" column="userId" />
</resultMap>
<select id="getUserAddressList" parameterType="Integer"
		resultMap="userAddressList">
		SELECT u.userName,u.id,a.id AS
		a_id,a.addressDesc,a.tel,a.contact
		FROM smbms_user u,smbms_address a
		WHERE a.userId=#{id} AND u.id=a.userId
</select>


